{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience the horror directly from a first-person perspective and enroll an adventure between you and a strong friendship with a tragic story.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A video report from the CPA (Central Paranormal Agency) shows an unknown person's perspective on a journey through the crowded and old walls of an abandoned house, hiding a dramatic and obscure story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2974100/extras/Description_Environment.gif?t=1733567065\" /> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Environment</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Set in a world where nightmares in real life are possible, and where the logics of steampunk/retro eras run the environment, players will embody the perspective of someone who will have to run, hide, and use different mechanics to survive the constant dread and danger of a creature, that emerges from anger and sadness, while trying to complete the main achievement.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2974100/extras/Description_Steampunk.gif?t=1733567065\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Mechanics</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use a variety of mechanics to guide you through mysterious hiding places and sense what lies beyond human sight. Avoid the various dangers lurking in the darkness in order to survive another day.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2974100/extras/Description_Mechanics.gif?t=1733567065\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2974100/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733567065","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2974100/page.bg.jpg?t=1733567065","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.